{
  "texts": [
    "LED volume productions (or virtual stage production (VSP)) have become popular, relying heavily on pre-production planning; hence there is potential for supporting tasks like pre-production shot visualization, or 3-D stage design.",
    "This area of research aligns well with 3-D capture and modeling research.",
    "Real-time 3-D view-synthesis (rendering) could also play a role in in-camera background projection for VSP.",
    "This will involve resolving high-resolution real-time rendering problems associated with projecting large live backgrounds.",
    "With the recent introduction of open-source pipelines for NeRF (Tancik et al. 2023; Li et al. 2023), modifying and testing different NeRFs has become trivial."
  ]
}